The tropical view directions set is two bands 8 samples offset 30 degree from
the equator, each with a 30 degree field of view:

  Yaw Pitch  Roll    FOV
    0    30     0     30
   45    30     0     30
   90    30     0     30
  135    30     0     30
  180    30     0     30
  225    30     0     30
  270    30     0     30
  315    30     0     30
    0   -30     0     30
   45   -30     0     30
   90   -30     0     30
  135   -30     0     30
  180   -30     0     30
  225   -30     0     30
  270   -30     0     30
  315   -30     0     30
